          "reviewBody": "This School at class 9 icse not offers subject choices updated. In group C of class 9 icse it not offers good scoring cputer science which is essential. At 78K per month , same group moulsari school offers more subject choices in class 9, 11 updated with NEP\n\nICSE board unregulated in UP by state , and by DOSEL eduMin both. So such subject choices un updated at class 9, 11 levels becomes compounding because of lack of.monitoring aspect.\n\nIn Social , disciplinary areas - school teacher presence ineffectiveness whether at Bus or in class  is NOT  enough self reviewed conservative manner. Slang excessive region with lot variety of attention seekers exist - such rounded ness absence on school own side compounds ineffective ness.\n\nIn SUPW side - efforts like Yamuna banks clear, kitchen garden at school and other such examples substanceful not inculcated.\n\nRunning 2 other boards in same school caused focus less on cicse",
